snippet.title: PROJECT SIX official title announcement and opening of the steam store.
snippet.description:
The mech action game [PROJECT SIX] has opened its steam store under the official title [OMEGA PHENEX COMMENCED PROJECT SIX].
メカアクションゲーム「PROJECT SIX」が、正式タイトル「OMEGA PHENEX COMMENCED PROJECT SIX」としてSteamストアをオープンしました。
#OMEGAPHENEX #オメガフェネクス #PROJECTSIX #プロジェクトシックス

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3392040/OMEGA_PHENEX_COMMENCED_PROJECT_SIX/
X(twitter):https://x.com/surumemanzyu
▼For those who want to try it out straight away　すぐに体験したい方向け
BOOTH :https://surumekoubou.booth.pm/items/1175114
